@page "/assistanceservice"

<PageTitle>ASSISTANCE SERVICE</PageTitle>

<div class="form-cont">
    <h2>EMPLOYMENT WELFARE AND ASSISTANCE SERVICE</h2>
    <p><strong>ABOUT THE SERVICE:</strong> NOC is one of the requirements for the conduct of recruitment activities by employment-providers (local companies or overseas employment agencies) thus expanding the existing employment facilitation service machinery of the Provincial Government.</p>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>OFFICE:</th>
            <td>Public Employment Service Office</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>CLASSIFICATION:</th>
            <td>Simple</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>TYPE OF TRANSACTION:</th>
            <td>G2C – Government to Citizen</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>WHO MAY AVAIL:</th>
            <td>All</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h3>CHECKLIST REQUIREMENTS</h3>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Requirement</th>
            <th>Where to Secure</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Any Valid Identification Card (ID)</td>
            <td>SSS, UMID, GSIS, Postal ID, etc.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Letter – Request of the OFW or Next of Kin (NOK)</td>
            <td>Provided by the client</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h3>PROCESS</h3>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>CLIENT STEPS</th>
            <th>AGENCY ACTION</th>
            <th>FEES TO BE PAID</th>
            <th>PROCESSING TIME</th>
            <th>PERSON RESPONSIBLE</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Sign in the Client Log Book and Present Identification Card</td>
            <td>Give the logbook to the Client.</td>
            <td>None</td>
            <td>1 min.</td>
            <td>Administrative Aide I</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Seek for assistance relative to OFW’s concerns and other related concerns</td>
            <td>Interview OFW or NOK and help the client accomplish the form (Client Profile and Employment Welfare Form).</td>
            <td>None</td>
            <td>20 mins.</td>
            <td>Administrative Aide I</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Request for Endorsement / Referral Letter to the agencies</td>
            <td>Prepare Endorsement / Referral Letter for various concerns (OWWA, DFA, DSWD, DOLE, Public Attorney’s Office).</td>
            <td>None</td>
            <td>5 mins.</td>
            <td>Labor and Employment Officer I, Asst. PESO Manager</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Release copy of Referral/Endorsement Letter</td>
            <td>Review and sign the Endorsement / Referral Letter.</td>
            <td>None</td>
            <td>1 min.</td>
            <td>PESO Manager</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Receive copy of Endorsement/Referral Letter</td>
            <td>Issue and accompany client to the concerned office.</td>
            <td>None</td>
            <td>1 min.</td>
            <td>Administrative Aide I</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p><strong>TOTAL: 28 minutes</strong></p>
    <p><em>End of Transaction</em></p>
</div>